		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">dougeff wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Looks good, I like the main character. His hair reminds me of Kid Niki.</div><br /><br />Kid Niki was definitely on my mind while I was drawing him!<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle">dullahan wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Cool. Interesting perspective for the platforms; will the player be able to move along a z-axis?</div><br /><br />Nope, 2D only. It's my half attempt to imitate Ninja Gaiden's pseudo 2.5D looking levels. I've gotten some feedback that it can look confusing, so I'm attempting to reduce that issue while still keeping it stylized.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
